            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry colname="c1">
                  <image href="../graphics/ZWCAD_UG_manual_2020_topic286_image004.png" />
                </entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </table>
 To create a cylinder
 as a three-dimensionalsurface</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Choose Draw &gt; Surfaces
 &gt; 3D Surfaces from the mainmenu.</li>
        <li>On the command line, type
 L (cyLinder).</li>
        <li>Specify the center, radius, andheight as describedpreviously.</li>
      </ol>
    </result>
